      • getAdditionalCustomerInformation

        public Map<String,String> getAdditionalCustomerInformation()
        Gets the additional customer information. The map will include the properties which will enable the user to provide additional information such as DOB, language preferences, different marketing options like opting-in to sms/email. (E.g.: "opt_in_sms":"true", "opt_in_email":"false"). To remove previously set information, an empty or null value with the key needs to be provided.
        Returns:
        the additional customer information
